      <title>普京称俄罗斯关押 6,465 名乌克兰战俘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/putin-says-russia-holds-6-465-ukrainian-prisoners-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·普京表示，俄罗斯关押了 6,465 名乌克兰战俘，而基辅当局还关押了 1,348 名俄罗斯人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/putin-says-russia-holds-6-465-ukrainian-prisoners-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 18:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
