    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在被定罪数周后出席知名首席执行官会议并发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/trump-to-speak-at-ceo-meeting-weeks-after-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将在美国大公司首席执行官组织商业圆桌会议上发表演讲。尽管最近被判定犯有重罪，但这位共和党预定的候选人仍将扩大与商界领袖的联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/trump-to-speak-at-ceo-meeting-weeks-after-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 18:37:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁支持蒂姆·斯科特试镜特朗普副总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/ellison-singer-boost-tim-scott-as-he-auditions-for-trump-vp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甲骨文公司联合创始人拉里·埃里森 (Larry Ellison) 和 Elliott Investment Management 的保罗·辛格 (Paul Singer) 都是某个政治倡导组织的财力雄厚的捐助者，该组织与共和党参议员蒂姆·斯科特 (Tim Scott) 关系密切，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 曾将蒂姆·斯科特列为潜在的竞选搭档。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/ellison-singer-boost-tim-scott-as-he-auditions-for-trump-vp</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:28:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>威尔士工党领袖因对斯塔默的打击而失去信任投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/welsh-labour-leader-loses-confidence-vote-in-blow-to-starmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威尔士首席大臣沃恩·格辛（Vaughan Gething）周三在一项不具约束力的不信任投票中落败，这对他领导的执掌地方政府的工党来说是一个打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/welsh-labour-leader-loses-confidence-vote-in-blow-to-starmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:25:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>YouGov 称法拉奇回归后改革党与保守党差距缩小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/farage-s-return-sees-reform-party-close-on-tories-yougov-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[YouGov 的一项新民意调查显示，脱欧顾问奈杰尔·法拉奇重返英国，担任改革英国领袖并参加下个月的大选。此举使得该右翼政党与首相里希·苏纳克领导的执政党保守党的差距仅缩小两个百分点，这对首相来说可能是一个糟糕的选举结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/farage-s-return-sees-reform-party-close-on-tories-yougov-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 16:40:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克总理指责反对派制造枪击事件，并警告称将有更多人受害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/slovak-premier-expects-to-return-to-work-in-weeks-after-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲佐上个月在一次暗杀行动中受重伤，他坚决表示最早本月返回工作岗位后将坚持其有时备受争议的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/slovak-premier-expects-to-return-to-work-in-weeks-after-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 15:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盟友警告称，中国对西方飞行员的争夺有增无减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/china-s-quest-for-western-pilots-is-unabated-us-and-allies-warn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其四个盟国周三在一份罕见的联合公报中警告称，中国招募西方退役军事飞行员训练其空军的努力仍在继续，这表明尽管中国一再努力打击这种做法，但北京方面仍不为所动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/china-s-quest-for-western-pilots-is-unabated-us-and-allies-warn</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗原子能监督机构谴责表明两国外交关系出现严重裂痕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/iran-censure-at-nuclear-watchdog-signals-deeper-diplomatic-rift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国原子能机构周三通过了一项对伊朗的谴责决议，加深了因伊朗伊斯兰共和国备受争议的核计划而产生的外交裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/iran-censure-at-nuclear-watchdog-signals-deeper-diplomatic-rift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 12:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥总统加尔维斯要求选举机构重新计算 80% 的选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/mexico-s-galvez-will-ask-electoral-body-to-recount-80-of-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥反对党领袖 Xochitl Galvez 表示，她将要求选举当局重新计算周日选举中 80% 的选票。在这场选举中，她输给了执政党候选人 Claudia Sheinbaum，失去了总统职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/mexico-s-galvez-will-ask-electoral-body-to-recount-80-of-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 03:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
